skdetail:

Invocation Name: funny burns
des: Try these lighthearted burns to add more fun to your day. When using the skill, you can say "Alexa, next" to move to the next burn. At any point, you can say "Alexa, stop" to exit the skill if the heat gets too intense.
priv: Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
